name: Serie Tribute: 08 - Iron Man
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

Iron Man is a superhero appearing in comic books published by Marvel Comics. He made his first appearance in Tales of Suspense #39 (March 1963), and received his own title in Iron Man #1 (May 1968).
Anthony Edward Stark, known as Tony Stark, is an American billionaire business tycoon, playboy and ingenious scientist, who suffered a serious chest injury during a kidnapping in the Middle East. When his captors try to force him to build a weapon of mass destruction, he instead creates a suit of armour to save his life and escape captivity. Stark later develops his suit, adding weapons and other technological devices he designed through his company, Stark Industries.
